title: SEP Sesam Backup Group Status
agents: sep_sesam
catalog: app/backup
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of SEP Sesam backup groups via the SEP Sesam
 REST API.

 The check maps the SEP Sesam result status to CheckMK states:
 SUCCESSFUL → OK, WARNING → WARN, ERROR → CRIT, CANCELLED → CRIT.
 Any other status results in UNKNOWN.

 Requires the SEP Sesam special agent to be configured for the host.

item:
 The name of the backup group as configured in SEP Sesam.

discovery:
 One service is created per backup group. Groups can be specified explicitly
 in the special agent rule or auto-discovered from the API list endpoint.
